            <br>
            
Welcome the Holiday Inn Ithaca, your ideal choice for Ithaca hotels. 
            The Holiday Inn Ithaca New York provides lodging in the Finger Lakes 
            Wine Region, one mile from Cornell University and Ithaca College.
<br> 
            <br>
            
<p>The <strong>Holiday Inn Ithaca</strong> has a full service restaurant <strong>Max's Classic American Grill</strong> <strong>and Sports Bar</strong> on site plus many more amenities you expect when you are traveling. There are lots of fun and historic places to visit while you are here. We can also accommodate your meeting, reception, reunion or banquet for up to 200 people. Our banquet facilities have just been newly renovated. So whether you are traveling on business or vacationing for pleasure, plan to stay at the <strong>Holiday Inn in Ithaca</strong>, New York. Our friendly staff is waiting for your arrival! <font color=#ff0000><br><br><strong>HIGH SPEED WIRELESS INTERNET ACCESS AVAILABLE THROUGHOUT THE HOTEL<br><br></strong></font><font color=#000000><a href="http://www.holidayinnupstatenewyork.com/" target=_blank>HOLIDAY INN UPSTATE NEW YORK</a></font></p>
<br>
